– Ada masalah?

679
00:52:53,410 --> 00:52:55,210
Sama sekali tidak!

680
00:53:15,450 --> 00:53:20,050
Kau sangat lambat. Cepatlah!

681
00:53:21,170 --> 00:53:22,570
Ya.

682
00:53:23,770 --> 00:53:27,770
